mixin Faq()
    section.container.faq
        h2 FAQs (Frequently Asked Questions)
        .accordion
            .accordion-item
                button.accordion-header
                    p What kind of products does NeatNest offer?
                .accordion-content
                    p NeatNest provides high-quality storage and organization products, including baskets, shelves, boxes, and space-saving solutions for every room. 
            .accordion-item
                button.accordion-header
                    p Do you offer international shipping?
                .accordion-content
                    p At the moment, our products are available for delivery within Karnataka, India. We are working on expanding our shipping options.
            .accordion-item
                button.accordion-header
                    p Can I return a product if it doesnâ€™t meet my expectations?
                .accordion-content
                    p Yes, we offer a hassle-free return policy. If you are not satisfied with your purchase, please contact us within 14 days to initiate a return.
            .accordion-item
                button.accordion-header
                    p How can I contact customer support?
                .accordion-content
                    p You can reach us via email at 
                        a(href='mailto:neatnest@gmail.com') neatnest@gmail.com  
                        We strive to respond as quickly as possible.

            .accordion-item
                button.accordion-header
                    p What is the estimated delivery time for my order?
                .accordion-content
                    p Delivery times depend on your location and the products ordered. Typically, deliveries within our service area take between 3-7 business days. For more accurate information, please contact our support team.
            .accordion-item
                button.accordion-header
                    p Do you offer gift wrapping services?
                .accordion-content
                    p At the moment, we do not offer gift wrapping. However, many of our storage products make for wonderful and stylish gifts right out of the box!
            .accordion-item
                button.accordion-header
                    p How can I track my order?
                .accordion-content
                    p Once your order has been shipped, you will receive an email with tracking information. You can use the tracking number to follow the progress of your delivery.
            .accordion-item
                button.accordion-header
                    p Can I change my order after it's been placed?
                .accordion-content
                    p We process orders quickly to ensure fast delivery. If you need to make changes, please contact us immediately after placing your order, and we will do our best to assist you.
            .accordion-item
                button.accordion-header
                    p Do you offer any discounts or promotions?
                .accordion-content
                    p From time to time, we offer special promotions and discounts. Be sure to check our website regularly or subscribe to our newsletter to stay updated on our latest offers.
            .accordion-item
                button.accordion-header
                    p What materials are your storage products made from?
                .accordion-content
                    p Our storage solutions are made from a variety of materials, including eco-friendly wood, durable metal, and high-quality fabrics. Each product is designed to be both functional and stylish.
            .accordion-item
                button.accordion-header
                    p Are your products environmentally friendly?
                .accordion-content
                    p Yes, we prioritize sustainability in our product designs. Many of our items are made with eco-friendly materials, and we strive to minimize our environmental impact at every step of the process.
            .accordion-item
                button.accordion-header
                    p Do you offer custom sizes for storage products?
                .accordion-content
                    p Currently, we do not offer custom sizes, but many of our products come in a variety of sizes to suit different needs. If you're looking for something specific, feel free to reach out to our team for assistance.
            .accordion-item
                button.accordion-header
                    p What should I do if my product is damaged during delivery?
                .accordion-content
                    p If your product arrives damaged, please contact us within 48 hours of delivery with photos of the damage. We will assist you with a replacement or return as per our return policy.
            .accordion-item
                button.accordion-header
                    p Can I pick up my order in person?
                .accordion-content
                    p At the moment, we do not offer in-person pickups. All orders are delivered directly to your location.